Come on, you bastards!

654
01:15:34,849 --> 01:15:36,544
And, those they dld trust--

655
01:15:36,617 --> 01:15:38,642
Come on, Comrades. Come on!

656
01:15:39,487 --> 01:15:40,511
Come on!

657
01:15:50,564 --> 01:15:51,997
Come on!

658
01:15:54,502 --> 01:15:55,662
Come on!

659
01:15:56,137 --> 01:15:58,833
Comrades! Earthshakers!

660
01:15:59,106 --> 01:16:01,199
Show them!

661
01:16:03,411 --> 01:16:05,436
Charge!

662
