1027
01:55:56,001 --> 01:55:58,196
Who did it, Comrade, the Whites?

1028
01:55:58,670 --> 01:55:59,830
The Whites?

1029
01:56:02,040 --> 01:56:03,940
No, Strelnikov.

1030
01:56:05,710 --> 01:56:08,235
Well, then, you must have done something.

1031
01:56:08,880 --> 01:56:10,677
lt wasn't us, Comrade.

1032
01:56:10,949 --> 01:56:13,417
The commander said
we'd sold horses to the Whites.

1033
01:56:13,485 --> 01:56:15,783
lt wasn't us, it was those pigs in Kuniko.

1034
01:56:15,921 --> 01:56:17,889
We told him, but he didn't believe us.

1035
01:56:17,956 --> 01:56:19,651
l expect you were lying.

1036
01:56:19,724 --> 01:56:21,885
-As God's my witness.
-But he isn't.

1037
01:56:23,929 --> 01:56:26,090
Commander Strelnikov is a great man.

1038
01:56:27,766 --> 01:56:31,293
A commander, Sasha,
and he lives on bread and water.

1039
01:56:31,903 --> 01:56:32,961
Does he?

1040
01:56:33,872 --> 01:56:35,339
l don't know. They say so.

1041
01:56:35,407 --> 01:56:36,396
lt's true.

1042
01:56:36,475 --> 01:56:38,534
No one knows where he comes from.

1043
01:56:39,044 --> 01:56:41,035
And they never know where he is.

1044
01:56:41,179 --> 01:56:43,409
-He's back up the line.
-Yes?

1045
01:56:46,451 --> 01:56:47,884
Someone's for it.

1046
01:56:50,455 --> 01:56:52,150
Oh, really, not again!

1047
01:56:53,758 --> 01:56:55,089
What this time?

1048
01:57:05,337 --> 01:57:07,999
Never mind, Father.
Get a good night's sleep.

1049
01:57:13,211 --> 01:57:15,008
l know what l'm going to do.

1050
01:57:37,769 --> 01:57:38,793
Look!

1051
01:57:39,971 --> 01:57:41,199
The Urals.

1052
01:57:43,074 --> 01:57:46,066
Look, Sasha, look.
That's where we're going, darling.

1053
01:57:46,411 --> 01:57:48,902
Through the mountains and into the forest.

1054
01:57:49,147 --> 01:57:51,138
Then it'll be much warmer still.

1055
01:57:52,384 --> 01:57:54,875
Will there be wolves in the forest?

1056
01:58:19,678 --> 01:58:21,270
Strelnikov!

1057
01:58:29,354 --> 01:58:30,844
That's Strelnikov.

